# Econvery Environment Configuration
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the values

# Currently, no environment variables are required as the OpenAlex API
# is free and doesn't require authentication.

# If you want to customize the polite email for OpenAlex API requests,
# you can set it here (optional):
# OPENALEX_EMAIL=your-email@example.com

# Future: If you plan to add Gemini API integration for AI features:
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key
